cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.SY

This paper proposes a novel approach for combining reinforcement learning and imitation learning in a scenario where only state sequences of an expert are available. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-category of Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed approach is evaluated on Atari games, which suggests that it may also belong to the sub-category of Computer Vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the approach involves optimizing the policy of the agent, which is a common task in Robotics (cs.RO) and Systems and Control (cs.SY). Therefore, these are the five most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
